@CVBackend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET {{CVBackend_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### GraphQL - Get All Companies
POST {{CVBackend_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ companies { id name position startDate endDate description } }"
}

###

### GraphQL - Get Single Company by ID
POST {{CVBackend_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query GetCompany($id: UUID!) { company(id: $id) { id name position startDate endDate description } }",
  "variables": {
    "id": "93f4aa3f-9808-4c58-b11d-e30dda4172fb"
  }
}

###

### GraphQL - Get Companies with Pagination
POST {{CVBackend_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query GetCompaniesPaged($first: Int!, $after: String) { companiesPaged(first: $first, after: $after) { edges { cursor node { id name position startDate endDate description } } pageInfo { hasNextPage hasPreviousPage startCursor endCursor } } }",
  "variables": {
    "first": 10,
    "after": null
  }
}

###

